            <title>[CASSANDRA-6464] Paging queries with IN on the partition key is broken</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6464</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Feels like MultiPartitionPager (which handles paging queries when there is a IN on the partition key) has completely missed &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5714&quot; title=&quot;Allow coordinator failover for cursors&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5714&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5714&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s train. As a result, it completely broken and will typically loop infinitely.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch to fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
